{
  "chapter": 234,
  "chapter_summary": "第234章《亲疏之别》分三条线展开。徐子陵离开梁都南下，途经荒山闻箫音，登山探寻，发现退隐二十年的四大魔头——丁九重、周老叹、金环真、尤鸟倦齐聚齐云观附近，皆为碧秀心之女石青璇而来，徐子陵决心暗中相助。寇仲在梁都与宣永商议攻取东海之策，宣永献计先取下邳控制骆马湖，断东海陆路交通。儿时玩伴桂锡良、幸容从竹花帮赶来，邵令周欲请寇仲回任帮主，寇仲警觉邵令周与李子通勾连，逼问二人立场，桂锡良坦言信寇仲多过邵令周，寇仲以亲疏之别定调，展开审问。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "宣永",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "以我们现在的实力，直接攻打东海，必是锻羽而归的结局。但若好好运用眼前的有利形势，说不定我们可不费一兵一卒，可把东海据为己有，少帅便不用长途跋涉的到飞马牧场招援。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yong",
      "text": "说来听听。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "宣永",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这湖叫骆马湖，乃河道交汇处，不但鱼产丰富，其湖岸区更良田万顷，是附近各乡县的命脉。只要攻占下邳，可控制此湖，那时不用少帅开声，附近的所有城郡都要乖乖归降。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yong",
      "text": "竟有这么便宜的事？下邳现在由谁人控制？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "宣永",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "下邳现落入了一批叫骆马帮的强徒手上，帮主叫都任，手下达三千之众，不但去打鱼的要向他缴交费用，连经过的船只旅客都要付买路钱，更不时四出抢掠，早弄得天怒人怨。假设我们能取而代之，又施行仁政，以少帅现时的威望，自是人心归向。到那时再取得东海西北的怀仁、琅琊、兰陵、良城四郡，及西南的沐阳、涟水、淮阳三郡，加上下邳，可完全断去东海郡的陆路交通，那时东海势成我们囊中之物。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yong",
      "text": "小永确是有见地的人，此计不但妙绝，且是我们力所能及的，对重建彭城更是大有帮助。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "宣永",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "如此下属立即派洛其飞到下邳摸清楚都任的底子，看看如何可一举把他除去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "见到你这小子真好，自听到你大败宇文化及的消息，我们立即兼程赶来，最怕你忽然又溜到别处去。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_rong",
      "speaker_name": "幸容",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "现在没多少人能像你和小陵那么出名了！唉！若早来两天便可见到小陵。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "两位大哥的消息确是灵通，小弟只踢了宇文化骨几下屁股都瞒不过你们，今趟有甚么可以提挈小弟？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "人说发财立品，你这家伙已是名满天下，可是骨子里那份赖皮却和以前毫无分别，就像是永不改变似的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "优良的本性是说改便能改的吗？像你这混蛋，当上个香主便四处充大哥，不也和你以前爱充场面一脉相承吗？分别只在你的是劣根性吧！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "大家一场兄弟，这么都不放过我？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_rong",
      "speaker_name": "幸容",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "也不知多久未试过笑得这么痛快！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "来！让小弟敬两位大哥一杯。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "今次我们赶来，实有至关紧要的事和你商量。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "以你现在的身份地位，总不会为鸡毛蒜皮的小事来找我？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 127
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你再耍我便揍你一顿，那管你为今有多厉害。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 129,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "桂大哥息怒，请问有何吩咐？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_rong",
      "speaker_name": "幸容",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "自当年在江阴城给你和小陵打得晴、雨、露三堂的人落花流水后，我们在邵军师的领导下整顿帮会，由于你和宋家的关系，良哥当上露竹堂堂主，嘿！小弟都捞了个副堂主来玩儿。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "我还知道锡良得到邵大小姐兰芳委身相许，唉！你这小子真个艳福不浅。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 137,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "又来耍我？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_rong",
      "speaker_name": "幸容",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "在宋家的支持下，这几年我们有很大的发展，重新在江都建立好地盘，否则也不能这么快得悉你和小陵先后大败李密和宇文化及的消息，帮内众兄弟都以你们为荣。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xing_rong",
      "text": "不要瞎捧，至少麦云飞那小子不会以我们为荣，对吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 147,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "理他个鸟！有邵军师作主，那轮得到他说话。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_rong",
      "speaker_name": "幸容",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "邵军师着我们来请你当帮主呢！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 157,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xing_rong",
      "text": "甚么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "自你和小陵刺杀任少名后，连带我们竹花帮亦声名大盛，不但不断有新人入帮，更有地方的小帮会主动要求和我们合并。说出来你或者仍不相信，现在长江一带谁不给我们几分面子，连李子通都要笼络我们。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "李子通？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_rong",
      "speaker_name": "幸容",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "邵军师和李子通很有交情，不过我们请你回去当帮主一事，却与李子通无关，而是帮中兄弟一致的决定。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "甚么事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_rong",
      "speaker_name": "幸容",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "甚么事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "你们究竟信我还是邵令周？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 185,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xing_rong",
      "speaker_name": "幸容",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "当然信你寇仲，我自少便知你和小陵最够义气。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "你在这里说的任何话，都不会有半句泄漏出去的，还怕他娘的什么？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "speaker_name": "桂锡良",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "他对我有提拔之恩，又肯把女儿嫁我，我…唉！当然是信你多一点啦。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_gui_xi_liang",
      "text": "总算你两个家伙明白亲疏之别。现在我们可以开始一个有趣的问答游戏，我问你答，若有任何隐瞒，最后的受害者必是你们无疑。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "周老叹",
      "listener": "char_ding_jiu_chong",
      "text": "丁九重终肯从你那地洞钻出来吗？希望你在那三十六招有所进展，免得到了地府去时而后悔无及哩！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_jiu_chong",
      "speaker_name": "丁九重",
      "listener": "char_zhou_lao_tan",
      "text": "不见周老叹兄足有二十年，想不到火气仍是这么大，难怪你的赤手掌始终不能达到登峰造极的境界，听说那贱人的女儿已得乃母真传，希望你不用饮恨齐云观内吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 225,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_lao_tan",
      "speaker_name": "周老叹",
      "listener": "char_ding_jiu_chong",
      "text": "过足了二十年瘾的丁大帝，竟沦落至给我轻轻一按，差点连卵蛋都给我挤出来，可笑啊！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_jiu_chong",
      "speaker_name": "丁九重",
      "listener": "char_zhou_lao_tan",
      "text": "我丁大帝新创的第三十七式'襄王有梦'滋味如何？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_huan_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "金环真",
      "listener": "char_ding_jiu_chong",
      "text": "我的大帝哥哥，老叹小弟，二十年了！仍要像当年那样甫见面便狗咬狗骨，不怕给我金环真扭耳朵儿吗？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhou_lao_tan",
      "speaker_name": "周老叹",
      "listener": "char_jin_huan_zhen",
      "text": "你要找人亲热，就找你的丁大帝吧！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_jiu_chong",
      "speaker_name": "丁九重",
      "listener": "char_jin_huan_zhen",
      "text": "老叹兄恁地好介绍，还是留给你吧！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_huan_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "金环真",
      "listener": "char_ding_jiu_chong",
      "text": "你们算是甚么东西，竟敢把我'媚娘子'金环真来个你推我让的。总有一天我要教你们跪在地上舐老娘的脚趾。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "尤鸟倦",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们不敢要你的，就让我'倒行逆施'尤鸟倦照单全收吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 234,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 309
    }
  ],
